{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/about/layout,_N_T_/about/page,_N_T_/about"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/about/__PAGE__","/about","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" imageSrcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" imageSrcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0sa1u0rc1hzk..css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/13-yp3opu.wcn.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0m_~xmh1tz_.k.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0m58q2exkjk_h.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0go48hnc0zwo..js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-147o_mzgf1hih.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/118bchv4m662w.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/10ncx8p1uu20r.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0g7j8a1sf-h~w.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>About | Tech 4 Underdogs</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Tech 4 Underdogs was built for small businesses the big firms overlook. 30+ years of combined experience in IT, web, and marketing — put to work for the businesses that need it most.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/images/cropped-Asset-16T4U.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"bg-navy overflow-hidden py-2.5 select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"animate-marquee whitespace-nowrap\"><span class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-white/80 text-xs tracking-[0.2em]\">MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  <!-- -->MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  MANAGED IT  •  SECURITY  •  WEB DESIGN  •  DEVELOPMENT  •  HOSTING  •  MARKETING  •  SEO  •  LOCAL VISIBILITY  •  </span></div></div><header class=\"bg-cream sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-navy/5\"><nav class=\"max-w-[1400px] mx-auto flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 lg:px-14\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a aria-label=\"Tech 4 Underdogs home\" class=\"flex-shrink-0\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Tech 4 Underdogs\" width=\"180\" height=\"58\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto w-36 lg:w-44\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 lg:gap-10\"><ul class=\"flex items-center gap-7 lg:gap-8\"><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li class=\"relative\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\">Services<svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 \"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"absolute top-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 pt-3 transition-all duration-200 opacity-0 invisible -translate-y-2 pointer-events-none\" role=\"menu\"><div class=\"bg-white border border-navy/10 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-3 w-[320px]\"><ul class=\"flex flex-col\"><li><a role=\"menuitem\" class=\"block px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/it-support\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">IT Support &amp; Security</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Monitoring, helpdesk, threat protection.</p></a></li><li><a role=\"menuitem\" class=\"block px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Local-SEO websites, custom builds, hosted by us.</p></a></li><li><a role=\"menuitem\" class=\"block px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">Online Marketing</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Local SEO, Google Ads, GBP management.</p></a></li></ul></div></div></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden w-11 h-11 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button></nav><div id=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out border-t border-navy/10 max-h-0\"><ul class=\"flex flex-col py-2 px-6 bg-cream\"><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-navy/5\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer\"><span>Services</span><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 \"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out max-h-0\"><ul class=\"pb-3 pl-3 border-l-2 border-orange/30 ml-1\"><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/it-support\">IT Support &amp; Security</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\">Online Marketing</a></li></ul></div></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"py-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary w-full justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></li></ul></div></header><main class=\"font-rajdhani\"><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>About Tech 4 Underdogs</p><h1 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7 break-words\">We built this for the<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy\">businesses</span> <!-- -->the big firms<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">overlook.</span></h1><div class=\"lg:hidden flex justify-center mb-8\"><img alt=\"Archie, the Tech 4 Underdogs mascot for small business\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[340px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"body-text lg:max-w-[500px] mb-9 text-[1.05rem]\">Tech 4 Underdogs is a technology, web, and marketing company built for small, locally-based businesses. With 30+ years of combined experience, we exist to give serious small business owners the reliable, affordable support they deserve.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary  justify-center sm:justify-start\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary  justify-center sm:justify-start\" href=\"/#services\">See How We Help<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex justify-end\"><img alt=\"Archie, the Tech 4 Underdogs mascot for small business\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[400px] xl:max-w-[440px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Small-Business.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"hidden lg:block absolute -left-8 top-12 text-orange/10 font-eurostile leading-none select-none pointer-events-none\" style=\"font-size:20rem;line-height:0.85\" aria-hidden=\"true\">*</div><div class=\"section-container section-y relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 lg:items-center\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Why we exist</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-6\">Most tech companies aren&#x27;t built for<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">small businesses.</span><br/><span class=\"italic text-navy\">We are.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text\">Small business owners run lean. No IT department down the hall, no marketing team on staff, no web developer on call. When something breaks, it falls on them — and the vendors meant to help often make things harder.</p></div><aside class=\"lg:pl-8 lg:border-l-4 lg:border-orange relative lg:max-w-[520px]\"><span class=\"hidden lg:block absolute -left-3 top-0 text-orange font-eurostile text-[2.5rem] leading-none bg-white px-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.4rem] sm:text-[1.55rem] lg:text-[1.7rem] leading-[1.25] mb-6 text-balance\">Small businesses are the<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">backbone</span> <!-- -->of local communities — and they deserve partners that take their needs<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">as seriously as they do.</span></p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/65 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.7] text-pretty\">We started Tech 4 Underdogs because that gap was too big to ignore. Same team, same care, every project — built around what actually moves the needle for the people doing the work.</p></aside></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-teal-gradient overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center lg:text-left\"><p class=\"eyebrow eyebrow-dark mb-5 justify-center lg:justify-start\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Experience that earns the right</p><p class=\"font-eurostile text-white leading-none mb-3 tabular-nums\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 11rem)\">30<span class=\"text-orange\">+</span></p><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-white text-[1.1rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide\">Years of combined experience</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-5\"><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-5 lg:p-6\"><p class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[1.85rem] lg:text-[2.4rem] leading-none mb-3 tabular-nums\">3</p><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-white text-[0.85rem] lg:text-[0.95rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 leading-tight\">Disciplines mastered</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-white/65 text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.5]\">IT · Web · Marketing</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-5 lg:p-6\"><p class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[1.85rem] lg:text-[2.4rem] leading-none mb-3 tabular-nums\">100%</p><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-white text-[0.85rem] lg:text-[0.95rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 leading-tight\">Small business focus</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-white/65 text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.5]\">By design, not default</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-5 lg:p-6\"><p class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[1.85rem] lg:text-[2.4rem] leading-none mb-3 tabular-nums\">1</p><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-white text-[0.85rem] lg:text-[0.95rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 leading-tight\">Team start to finish</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-white/65 text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.5]\">Same people, every project</p></div></div><p class=\"body-text body-text-dark\">Three decades in the trenches of design, technology, and marketing. That experience doesn&#x27;t go to a big-agency client list — it goes to work for<!-- --> <span class=\"text-white font-semibold\">your business.</span></p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Who we&#x27;re built for</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7\">We don&#x27;t serve<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">everyone.</span><br/>We serve the ones the big firms<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">overlook.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text mb-6\">Large IT firms and marketing agencies are built for large clients. Their pricing, processes, and attention reflect that. Small businesses — 2 employees or 20, real community footprint — get handed off to junior staff or priced out entirely.</p><p class=\"tagline text-navy\">We stay focused.<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">That&#x27;s why we&#x27;re good at it.</span></p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\"></line><path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Priced for Small Business</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">No enterprise pricing, no minimum retainers sized for large firms. Packages built around what small businesses actually need — and can afford.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">A Real Person. Every Time.</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">No call centers. When something needs attention, you reach someone who already knows your business — not someone reading from a script.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">We Stay With You</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">We don&#x27;t disappear after the first invoice. Our model is built on long-term relationships — because that&#x27;s when we actually become useful.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center\"><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 order-2 lg:order-1\"><li class=\"flex gap-5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-5 lg:p-6\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</span><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.25rem] lg:text-[1.4rem] mb-2 tracking-wide leading-tight\">Reliability over promises.</h3><p class=\"body-text\">We don&#x27;t oversell what we can do. We show up, do the work, and make sure your systems, your website, and your marketing keep working — day after day.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-5 lg:p-6\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">02</span><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.25rem] lg:text-[1.4rem] mb-2 tracking-wide leading-tight\">Clarity over jargon.</h3><p class=\"body-text\">You shouldn&#x27;t need a translator to understand your own technology. We explain things plainly, keep you informed, and never hide behind complexity.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-5 lg:p-6\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</span><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.25rem] lg:text-[1.4rem] mb-2 tracking-wide leading-tight\">Loyalty over transactions.</h3><p class=\"body-text\">We&#x27;re most useful when we&#x27;ve been with you long enough to know your business. We&#x27;re in your corner for the long haul — not just until the contract renews.</p></div></li></ul><div class=\"order-1 lg:order-2\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>How we work</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-6\">We take<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">three things</span> <!-- -->seriously.<br/><span class=\"italic text-navy\">Everything else follows.</span></h2><p class=\"tagline text-navy\">Calm. Capable.<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">In your corner.</span></p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"\"><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between gap-6 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"h-compact text-balance text-navy\">What<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">small business</span> <!-- -->owners<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">say.</span></h2><p class=\"eyebrow flex-shrink-0 \"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Real words from real owners</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><ul class=\"overflow-hidden\"><li class=\"block\"><figure class=\"bg-white border-navy/10 shadow-sm border rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.15rem] leading-[1.7] mb-7 text-pretty text-navy/85\">[Placeholder testimonial — replace with a real client quote about how Tech 4 Underdogs solved an actual problem.]</blockquote><figcaption><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-0.5 text-orange\">[First L.]</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-xs tracking-wide uppercase text-navy/55\">[Business name]<!-- --> · [Owner]</p></figcaption></figure></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hidden\"><figure class=\"bg-white border-navy/10 shadow-sm border rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.15rem] leading-[1.7] mb-7 text-pretty text-navy/85\">[Placeholder testimonial — replace with a real client quote about responsiveness and the no-pressure feel.]</blockquote><figcaption><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-0.5 text-orange\">[First L.]</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-xs tracking-wide uppercase text-navy/55\">[Business name]<!-- --> · [Owner]</p></figcaption></figure></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hidden\"><figure class=\"bg-white border-navy/10 shadow-sm border rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-orange text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.15rem] leading-[1.7] mb-7 text-pretty text-navy/85\">[Placeholder testimonial — replace with a real client quote about value compared to bigger firms.]</blockquote><figcaption><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-0.5 text-orange\">[First L.]</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-xs tracking-wide uppercase text-navy/55\">[Business name]<!-- --> · [Owner]</p></figcaption></figure></li></ul></div><div class=\"flex justify-center gap-2.5 mt-8\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Testimonial pagination\"><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-label=\"Show testimonial 1\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"h-2.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer bg-orange w-8\"></button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-label=\"Show testimonial 2\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"h-2.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer bg-navy/25 hover:bg-navy/50 w-2.5\"></button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-label=\"Show testimonial 3\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"h-2.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer bg-navy/25 hover:bg-navy/50 w-2.5\"></button></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about-cta\" class=\"section-y scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden bg-teal-gradient\"><div class=\"section-container\"><div class=\"max-w-[760px] mx-auto text-center\"><p class=\"eyebrow eyebrow-dark mb-5 justify-center\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Let&#x27;s have a real conversation</p><h2 class=\"h-section mb-6\"><span class=\"text-white\">If you&#x27;re tired of vendors who don&#x27;t </span><span class=\"italic text-white\">show up,</span><br/><span class=\"text-white\">let&#x27;s </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">talk.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text body-text-dark mb-9 max-w-[560px] mx-auto\">No pressure. No pitch. Just a straightforward conversation about your technology, your website, or your marketing — and whether we&#x27;re the right fit to help.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-6\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-lg justify-center border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10\" href=\"/#services\">See How We Help <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-white/55 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase\">We respond within one business day. No sales pressure, ever.</p></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-white border-t border-navy/10\"><div class=\"section-container pt-16 pb-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1.2fr] gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-start\"><div><img alt=\"Tech 4 Underdogs\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"58\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto w-40 mb-4\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.9rem] leading-[1.7] max-w-[320px] mb-6\">Reliable, affordable IT, websites, and online marketing — built for the small businesses doing serious work.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.8rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-5\">Navigate</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\"><li><a class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/65 text-[0.9rem] hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center gap-2.5 leading-snug cursor-pointer\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-orange text-[8px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">■</span>Home</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/65 text-[0.9rem] hover:text-orange tra